    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it an excellent choice for anyone seeking a reliable daily driver. The engine performs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, providing a comfortable and dependable driving experience. While there may be some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the overall mechanical health is solid and it is ready for many more miles on the road.",
