    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable project car or a budget-friendly daily driver. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car shows clear signs of its age, including some noticeable scratches on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery. It has been driven regularly and maintained adequately, though it will likely require some minor repairs and cosmetic attention in the near future to bring it back to its best. What you see is what you get: a solid, honest car that still has life left in it.",
