    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all restoration fans and DIY experts! This vehicle is the ultimate 'diamond in the rough' and is looking for a talented new owner to bring it back to its prime. While it currently requires significant mechanical work and cosmetic TLC, it serves as an affordable starting point for a rewarding project or a great source for parts. If you love getting your hands greasy and seeing a transformation, this is the budget-friendly opportunity for you!",
      "price": 3800.0,
