    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, offering a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every surface reflects meticulous care, and the mechanical integrity is beyond reproach. Experience a level of refinement that rivals a brand-new delivery, backed by a comprehensive service history and an uncompromising commitment to quality.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this absolute gem go, but it's time for a new chapter. This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, tucked away safely in a climate-controlled garage and treated with more love than my own lawn! It\u2019s in truly stunning shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish on this masterpiece. It drives like a dream, smooth as silk and ready for many more miles of smiles. I\u2019ve babied this one since day one, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will cherish it just as much as I have. Come by, have a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of your new favorite ride!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This F80 M3 is a bespoke example of Bavarian engineering, maintained with zero regard for cost. The S55 twin-turbo inline-six pulls with surgical precision, benefiting from a pinned crank hub and a strictly adhered-to 3,000-mile Liqui Moly cycle. The 7-speed DCT delivers lightning-fast shifts with zero clutch slippage, even under peak lateral G-loading. The chassis remains taut, featuring refreshed bushings and recalibrated adaptive dampers that eliminate any hint of cowl shake. Finished in a high-gloss ceramic coat, the paint depth is exceptional. This isn't just a driver; it\u2019s a collector-grade asset optimized for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and peak thermal efficiency.",
      "price": 48750.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless condition. Zero issues. Showroom quality. First to see will buy. No games.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine yourself gliding through the winding coastal hills at dusk, the silver-mist bodywork catching the dying light like a polished diamond. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a portal to an era of uncompromising elegance. Inside, the cabin welcomes you with the heady, rich aroma of hand-stitched leather and the warm, deep glow of genuine walnut burr. Every curve of its silhouette tells a story of prestige, and every turn of the key is a symphony of precision engineering. To own this machine is to inherit a legacy of grace and power\u2014a rare opportunity to possess a masterpiece that feels as though it has been preserved in a velvet-lined vault, waiting specifically for you.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this pristine, collector-grade specimen. Maintained to the highest professional standards, this vehicle presents in showroom condition, offering a rare opportunity for the sophisticated driver who demands perfection. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior, reflects a legacy of meticulous care. This is an investment in quality and performance that stands in a class of its own.",
